# Large data / model outputs -- not meant for git, regenerated or fetched locally.
# (Neither has ever been tracked, but nothing was previously stopping `git add -A`
# from sweeping in ~3 GB of GLanCE data + trained models.)
Data/
Model_Outputs/
CCDC_Outputs/

# Credentials. Blanket *.json is deliberate: a future `gcloud iam service-accounts
# keys create` can name its output file anything, so a name-pattern guess (e.g.
# *service-account*.json) is not reliable protection. No other *.json is currently
# tracked or needed in this repo -- if one legitimately needs to be committed later,
# add a `!path/to/file.json` line to re-include it explicitly.
*.json
*.pem
*.key
.env

# Local tool config -- machine-specific, not shared project state.
.claude/
.ipynb_checkpoints/
__pycache__/
*.pyc
.DS_Store

# Docker build artifacts (none currently produced locally, but keep tarballs out
# if `docker save` is ever used instead of pushing to Artifact Registry).
*.tar
